eu.cqse.check.framework.typetracker.clike

Class CLikeTypeInfoExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.cqse.check.framework.typetracker.TypeInfoExtractorBase
      • eu.cqse.check.framework.typetracker.clike.CLikeTypeInfoExtractor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITypeInfoExtractor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CsTypeInfoExtractor, JavaTypeInfoExtractor

    public abstract class CLikeTypeInfoExtractor
extends TypeInfoExtractorBase
    The clike type info extractor is an abstract base class for type info extractors for clike languages. Type information in clike languages is only introduces by shallow entities that are either statements, methods or attributes. Other shallow entity types don't introduce any type information.

      • extractFromForLikeTokens

        protected List<TypedVariable> extractFromForLikeTokens(ShallowEntity entity,
                                                       eu.cqse.check.framework.scanner.ETokenType endToken)
        Extracts type information from the start tokens of for, foreach and using statements. The given end token type is used to determine the end of the variable declaration within the loop. For loops use SEMICOLON, while foreach loops use IN and using statements use RPAREN.
